    <item>
      <title>1 Heart Challenge (1.6.0)</title>
      <author>Xovtar</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/582966</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/582966#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">3de6a0ffd8ea2594bfe84a12e13b2d758815cf47</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 00:47:51 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67ddf1098ada8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67ddf133439bb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67ddf14320f58.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67ddf15187afe.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67ddf16cd84d5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67ddf17b275ce.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;Updated version of the mod for the website.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;Ready to prove you're a true Hylian warrior? The &lt;strong data-start="222" data-end="243"&gt;1 Heart Challenge&lt;/strong&gt; save throws you straight into the wilds of Hyrule with just &lt;strong data-start="304" data-end="315"&gt;1 heart&lt;/strong&gt;, minimal gear, and no mercy. This isn’t your average stroll through the kingdom – it's survival of the fittest. Can you conquer Ganon without boosting your health?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
Perfect for seasoned adventurers or those looking to test their limits, this save is the ultimate way to replay &lt;em data-start="593" data-end="613"&gt;Breath of the Wild&lt;/em&gt; with a brutal twist.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&lt;strong data-start="636" data-end="654"&gt;Save Features:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&lt;ul data-start="655" data-end="823"&gt;&#13;
&lt;li data-start="655" data-end="697"&gt;Just &lt;strong data-start="662" data-end="673"&gt;1 Heart&lt;/strong&gt; – no room for mistakes.&lt;/li&gt;&#13;
&lt;li data-start="698" data-end="760"&gt;Basic starter gear – enough to get going, but far from safe.&lt;/li&gt;&#13;
&lt;li data-start="761" data-end="823"&gt;Hyrule is untouched – all shrines, towers, and quests await.&lt;/li&gt;&#13;
&lt;/ul&gt;&#13;
&lt;strong data-start="825" data-end="868"&gt;Challenge Ideas (Make It Even Harder!):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&lt;ul data-start="869" data-end="1204"&gt;&#13;
&lt;li data-start="869" data-end="967"&gt;&lt;strong data-start="871" data-end="889"&gt;No Teleporting&lt;/strong&gt; – Fast travel is off-limits. Explore the world on foot, like a true survivor.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-start="869" data-end="967" class="SelectedElement"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Starting Gear Only &lt;/b&gt;- Play with what you started with. Requires additional mods mentioned below. *I've pre compiled the mods in the downloads*&lt;/li&gt;&#13;
&lt;li data-start="968" data-end="1029"&gt;&lt;strong data-start="970" data-end="982"&gt;No Armor&lt;/strong&gt; – Only your skill and timing will protect you.&lt;/li&gt;&#13;
&lt;li data-start="1030" data-end="1075"&gt;&lt;strong data-start="1032" data-end="1046"&gt;No Cooking&lt;/strong&gt; – Raw food only. Heal smart.&lt;/li&gt;&#13;
&lt;li data-start="1076" data-end="1126"&gt;&lt;strong data-start="1078" data-end="1097"&gt;Permadeath Rule&lt;/strong&gt; – Die once, delete the save.&lt;/li&gt;&#13;
&lt;li data-start="1127" data-end="1204"&gt;&lt;strong data-start="1129" data-end="1149"&gt;Master Mode Only&lt;/strong&gt; – Enemies regenerate, and you have 1 heart. Good luck.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;*Can be played with other challenging mods for a more challenging playthrough.*&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul data-start="869" data-end="1204"&gt;&#13;
&lt;/ul&gt;&#13;
Whether you're a streamer looking for intense content, or a hardcore player looking to reignite your passion for the game, this save offers a fresh and savage twist on one of the greatest open-world adventures.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Additional Recommendations:&lt;br&gt;*These mods are not required but highly recommended for one of the challenges if you choose to do that challenge.*&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;BCML: BOTW Cross-Platform Mod Loader: https://gamebanana.com/tools/6849&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Weapon Durability x2: https://gamebanana.com/mods/388039&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Instructions For Implementing the&#13;
MOD Pack I Provided&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
